<%- include("templates/afterLoginHeader") %>
  <div style="height: 150px;"></div>

  <div class="container-fluid my-5">
    <h1 class="text-primary text-center mb-5">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <div class="accordion" id="faq-accordion">
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1"
            aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1">
            What is the Meal Genie app, and how does it work?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse fs-5" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#faq-accordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Meal Genie is a personalized recipe app that uses advanced algorithms and AI to provide health-conscious
            foodies with new recipe suggestions based on their dietary preferences and cooking skills. The app helps
            users make informed and healthy food choices by providing tailored recipe options and ingredient
            suggestions.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2"
            aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
            Can I customize my recipes based on my dietary restrictions and preferences?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse fs-5" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#faq-accordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes, Meal Genie allows users to customize their recipe suggestions based on their dietary preferences and
            restrictions, such as vegan, gluten-free, or low-carb.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3"
            aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
            Is Meal Genie free to use or does it require a subscription fee?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse fs-5" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#faq-accordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes, Meal Genie is completely free to use and doesn't require any subscription. Users can download the app
            for free and access all of its features, including personalized recipe suggestions without any additional
            cost.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4"
            aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
            Are the recipes provided by the Meal Genie app easy to follow?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse fs-5" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#faq-accordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes, the recipes provided by the Meal Genie app are easy to follow, and they include step-by-step
            instructions and photos to guide you through the cooking process.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq5">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5"
            aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
            How does Meal Genie ensure the accuracy of its ingredient suggestions?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse fs-5" aria-labelledby="faq5" data-bs-parent="#faq-accordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Meal Genie uses a combination of user feedback, nutrition data, and machine learning algorithms to suggest
            ingredients that are both healthy and appropriate for the selected dietary preferences. The app also allows
            users to add and remove ingredients from the suggested recipes based on their individual preferences and
            taste.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="height: 300px;"></div>



  <%- include("templates/footer") %>

